{{version025}}
{{Flavour|Causes a nearby ally to fly into a berserk rage. Going berserk temporarily increases health, speed, and damage dealt in melee.}}
'''Berserk Other''' is a monster-only spell which allows a monster to send other monsters [[berserk]]. This makes it a pure support spell, and one whose threat level is entirely dependent on how dangerous the nearby monsters are. Queen bees can only use this spell on [[killer bee]]s and [[meliai]], while moths of wrath can target any monster that is allowed to go berserk.

